OL,3,CHorizon scandal: Post Office should
OL,4,Cpay for therapy, say sub-postmasters
OL,6,FThere are calls for the Post Office to
OL,7,Fpay for therapy and mental health
OL,8,Ftreatment for sub-postmasters and
OL,9,Ftheir families. ITV News
OL,10,FInvestigations Editor Daniel Hewitt
OL,11,Freports on the devastating impact the
OL,12,Fscandal has had on the lives of some
OL,13,Fof the victims
OL,15,FWrongly accused and wrongly convicted
OL,16,FSubpostmasters have said the Post
OL,17,FOffice should pay for therapy and
OL,18,Fcounselling "for life" due to the
OL,19,Fongoing trauma caused by the Horizon
OL,20,FIT Scandal.
