OL,3,CHorizon scandal: Post Office should
OL,4,Cpay for therapy, say sub-postmasters
OL,6,FParmod Kalia ran a Post Office Branch
OL,7,Fin Orpington in Kent for over a decade
OL,8,Fwhen he was wrongly accused of theft
OL,9,Fin 2001. The father of four was
OL,10,Fsentenced to six months in prison and
OL,11,Fforced to pay #22,000 to the Post
OL,12,FOffice despite there being no proof he
OL,13,Fstole it.
OL,15,FHe says the conviction destroyed his
OL,16,Flife and nearly cost him his marriage.
OL,17,FHe told ITV News he sought therapy
OL,18,Fafter attempting to take his own life.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/21
