OL,3,CHorizon scandal: Post Office should
OL,4,Cpay for therapy, say sub-postmasters
OL,6,FTracey Merritt was accused of stealing
OL,7,Fmoney in 2009 from the two Post
OL,8,FOffices she ran in Somerset with her
OL,9,Fdaughter Lisa. Tracey spoke to
OL,10,Fresearchers from UCL and the
OL,11,FUniversity of Exeter about her
OL,12,Fexperience for this new study.
OL,14,FShe was threatened with prosecution,
OL,15,Fand told Lisa would be too if she did
OL,16,Fnot cut off contact with her. As a
OL,17,Fresult, Tracey didn't see her daughter
OL,18,Ffor 18 months.
