OL,6,F"They took my everything. Absolutely
OL,7,Feverything. They took away the person
OL,8,FI am."
OL,10,F"I've got PTSD so I need to be able to
OL,11,Fdeal with that because that's a scary
OL,12,Fplace to be... I've been told I have
OL,13,Fto have some serious help but that
OL,14,Fcosts money which I have to pay for
OL,15,Fout of my compensation, but I haven't
OL,16,Fhad that compensation."
OL,18,F"They are still messing with our
OL,19,Flives, so yes, they should (pay for
OL,20,Ftherapy)."
