OL,3,CHorizon scandal: Post Office should
OL,4,Cpay for therapy, say sub-postmasters
OL,6,FProfessor Richard Moorhead, who leads
OL,7,Fthe Post Office Project and co-
OL,8,Fauthored the study alongside Dr Sally
OL,9,FDay and Dr Karen Nokes at UCL and and
OL,10,FProfessor Rebecca Helm at Exeter, told
OL,11,FITV News that the long process of
OL,12,Freceiving full and final compensation
OL,13,Fwas contributing to the trauma
OL,14,Fexperienced by sub-postmasters.
OL,16,F"It feels like to the sub-postmasters,
OL,17,Ffighting over every detail. Making
OL,18,Fthem re-prove that things went wrong
OL,19,Fand that they have been harmed,"
OL,20,FProfessor Moorhead said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/21
