OL,3,CHorizon scandal: Post Office should
OL,4,Cpay for therapy, say sub-postmasters
OL,6,F"It's those sorts of things that have
OL,7,Fincreased the cycle of pain for these
OL,8,Fpeople... These people are likely to
OL,9,Fneed help for a long time and it's
OL,10,Freally important that they get all the
OL,11,Fhelp they need to deal with this."
OL,13,F"It's enormous," Sir Alan Bates, long-
OL,14,Ftime campaigner for sub-postmasters,
OL,15,Fsays of the psychological impact of
OL,16,Fthe scandal.
OL,18,F"It's not just the sub-postmasters who
OL,19,Fhave been (impacted) by this. It goes
OL,20,Fright across the families. It's
OL,21,Fhorrendous."
