OL,6,FParmod Kalia is one of the sub-
OL,7,Fpostmasters still suffering as a
OL,8,Fresult of the scandal. He is one of
OL,9,Fmore than 4,300 subpostmasters still
OL,10,Fawaiting full and final compensation.
OL,11,FDiagnosed with cancer two and a half
OL,12,Fyears ago, he believes his final
OL,13,Fredress payment may come too late.
OL,15,F"I'm taking it one day at a time,"
OL,16,Fformer sub-postmaster tells ITV News
OL,17,Fas he waits for his final redress
OL,18,Fpayment.
