OL,6,F"I've been undergoing treatment...
OL,7,FEvery day I wake up in the morning, I
OL,8,Fthank God I've got another day. I
OL,9,Fdon't know about my own personal
OL,10,Fhealth, how long it's going to be, how
OL,11,Flong it's going to last, but I'm just
OL,12,Ftaking it one day at a time," he says.
