OL,7,F"generational trauma caused from the
OL,8,Fscandal needs to be recognised,
OL,9,Faddressed, and appropriately responded
OL,10,Fto. Partners, children and now even
OL,11,Fgrandchildren of SPMs live in the
OL,12,Fshadow cast on the first victims of
OL,13,Fthe Post Office Scandal."
